Hey Chelsea Family,

Me and my family have recently come under serious financial constraints, so much to the point where we’ve been late on tuition payments. This has resulted in me being withdrawn from my course it is however reversible subject to the outstanding fee being paid in full at once. This has been a very stressful situation for us that’s been going on for months and has now become a serious deciding factor in my quest to graduate come July. I’m unable to go to class, log in to my uni account, or access my campuses unless it is paid.

Creating a crowdfunding campaign was the last thing I wanted to do to try and combat this. However, I’m left with little to no options at this point, It is somewhat of an urgent matter and I’ll be dammed if I don’t graduate because of financial difficulties, I won’t give up without a fight.

Thanks for taking the time out of your busy schedules to read this, please if you know anyone that can contribute I encourage you to please share it with them, all support is greatly appreciated.

Love, from Ki 💙
